The paper focuses on learning robotic skills from raw image observations, which is a core topic in robotics (cs.RO). The paper also proposes a self-supervised algorithm for learning image registration, which involves computer vision techniques (cs.CV). The paper utilizes machine learning techniques for learning robotic skills, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with closed-loop robotic manipulation, which involves control systems (cs.SY).
